name: プロデューサー
text:
……
いいステージだよ、すごく
trans:
...
It was a really good performance.

name: 透
text:
まあ、いるし。みんなも
それに────
trans:
Well, I am. So is everyone.
And anyway────

name: 透
text:
でも
考えなくてよくなる
trans:
But,
it helps not thinking about it.

name: 透
text:
わかるんだ、ここなら
どうすればいいか
trans:
At least I know what to do.
When I'm here.
